reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This sign is really cute and I love it!! I have 3 kids and we used to listen to 3 little birds and read the 3 little birds book when my two younger kids were toddlers so when I saw this, I was so happy to get this to display in my house. I would recommend this.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Really cute little decorative sign.
reviews.reviewText: I got this because the birds match a larger piece of decor on my wall. I put it on a shelf of my TV stand alongside a potted succulent. It looks very nice. The font is done nicely on a painted wood surface. Cute and inexpensive piece of decor.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is absolutely perfect! Small and sweet, does not take up much room but carries a big message of hope and positivity. Print and picture are clear and crisp, box stands without assistance, and fits just about anywhere. Makes a nice gift too. Price is great. Would recommend in a heartbeat, love this piece.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Charming Piece with an Endearing Message
reviews.reviewText: Everyone benefits from sweet words and enchanting messages to stir positive thoughts and joyful feelings. This is a lovely little desk piece that doesn't take up much room. The design is creative and stirring. The box balances well and can be easily moved around to find the right space. The message is a meaningful reminder to help quell stress, anxiety, and panic. I think its can be delightful little gift to someone who may struggle a bit - giving them enduring assurance that you care.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute sign for desk, shelf or wall
reviews.reviewText: This small 5-inch by 5-inch sign is perfect for adding go your gallery art wall, desk top, or your shelf. The print is clear and quality. The finish is almost matte-like, so while I was going to place in the bathroom, I'm not sure of it's water resistance from splashes. Very happy with this sign as the saying means something to me as well, so happy to have it in my home.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars three little birds
reviews.reviewText: This sign is simple and sweet. It's got 3 little bird silhouettes on it and Bob's famous line. The printing is clear and it's altogether a lovely image. This quote has special meaning to me and I'm glad to have it on a little sign I can set on my mantle. It would go great on a desk too. Note that at 5 x 5 inches it is quite small; I was aware of that so it's not an issue. I'm very happy with it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is a cute little plaque. I love the saying and the font it is written in. It is solid and looks nice.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Adorable Little Sign
reviews.reviewText: We all need a little daily reminder that everything will be okay. This little sign is adorable with the birds, but also small enough to put in a place to see every day. There are no spelling mistakes and the images are clear.
